Agent Test Results Overview
All four agents failed this task:

codex-gpt5: FAIL (BAD FAILURE - Underspecified instruction + Environment issues)
claude-sonnet-4-5: FAIL (BAD FAILURE - Underspecified instruction + Environment issues)
